title: North Star Records Christmas Collection - Folk
description:
A collection of Christmas CDs from North Star Records. North Star was a New England Folk label that sadly went out of business a few years ago, so these CDs are currently out of print. A number of these were sold during Christmastime at Nature Company stores back in the 1990s. Relaxing instrumental folk arrangements on piano, guitar, flute, harp, dulcimer, and other traditional instruments.
